@startuml Payment_Saga_Sequence
title Payment Saga - Диаграмма последовательности

participant "Kafka (TripCompleted)" as trigger
participant "Payments Service (Orchestrator)" as payments #LightGreen
participant "Fraud Service" as fraud
participant "Яндекс Пэй" as yandex_pay
participant "Notification Service" as notification

trigger -> payments: TripCompleted event
activate payments

== Шаг 1: Инициация платежа ==
payments -> payments: InitiatePaymentCmd (статус: PENDING)

== Шаг 2: Проверка на фрод ==
payments -> fraud: CheckPaymentFraudCmd
activate fraud
fraud --> payments: FraudCheckPassed
deactivate fraud

== Шаг 3: Списание с карты пассажира ==
payments -> yandex_pay: ChargePassengerCmd (amount: 450₽)
activate yandex_pay
yandex_pay --> payments: PaymentCompleted
deactivate yandex_pay

== Шаг 4: Расчет заработка водителя ==
payments -> payments: CalculateEarningsCmd (450₽ - 20% комиссия = 360₽)

== Шаг 5: Зачисление на баланс водителя ==
payments -> payments: CreditDriverBalanceCmd (+360₽ на баланс)

== Шаг 6: Уведомление ==
payments ->> notification: NotifyPaymentCmd
activate notification
notification --> notification: Push пассажиру: "Списано 450₽"
notification --> notification: Push водителю: "Начислено 360₽"
deactivate notification

payments -> payments: PaymentSaga COMPLETED
deactivate payments

== Сценарий ошибки: Платежный шлюз ==

note over payments, yandex_pay
  При ChargeError:
  Retry 3 раза (5s, 15s, 30s)
  -> Если не удалось:
    MarkPaymentPendingCmd
    + Celery retry через 1 час
end note

== Сценарий ошибки: Фрод ==

note over payments, fraud
  При FraudDetected:
  CancelPaymentCmd -> CANCELLED_FRAUD
  + HoldBookingCmd -> расследование
  + Notify -> "Платеж заблокирован"
end note

@enduml
